Emily Berrington https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emily_Berrington 0 Emily Berrington (born 7 December 1986) is an English actress who played Simone Al-Harazi in 24: Live Another Day (2014) and Niska in the Channel 4 and AMC TV series Humans (2015–).
